        <item>
          <title>Mac Security Alert: New BanShee Stealer Malware Targets Browser Credentials and Cryptocurrency Wallets</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A new variant of info-stealer malware, BanShee, has been discovered targeting Mac users. The malware uses phishing websites and fake GitHub repositories to steal browser credentials, cryptocurrency wallets, and other personal data.]]></description>
